---
title: HelloHero: American Baked Lamb with Herb-Roasted Veggies, Slaw & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Load up lamb with flavour before baking it until golden and tender. Smokey All-American spice blend and a creamy dill-parsley slaw will combine to make a sensational dinner that everyone will happily devour!

